commit.message:
ebuild: Do not output empty CRATES=""

Put a newline in CRATES="" when it ought to be empty, as otherwise
cargo.eclass will reject the ebuild as having no CRATES defined.

Signed-off-by: Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org>
